le 1-2 tbsp of the reserved ginger sauce over salmon. Weigh zucchini into Varoma."},{"content":"Arrange zucchini and broccolini around salmon in Varoma, secure Varoma lid and cook <b>6 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Weigh bok choy into Varoma and arrange around salmon and other vegetables in the Varoma, secure Varoma lid and cook <b>5-7 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>, or until salmon and vegetables are cooked to your liking."},{"content":"Drizzle remaining ginger sauce over salmon and vegetables, sprinkle with spiced cashews and serve immediately."}],"hintsAndTricks":["For thick salmon fillets you may need to cook 3-4 minutes first before adding the zucchini and broccolini and proceeding as per recipe.","Cook fish to an internal temperature of 145°F or until flesh is opaque and separates easily with a fork.","Serve with jasmine rice, brown rice or vermicelli noodles.","Szechuan peppercorns, Chinese five spice and bok choi can be found in specialty grocery stores and Asian supermarkets.","Bok choy can be replaced with Pak choi."],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","45m","4 portions"]}